### GET all literature types
GET http://localhost:8080/api/literature-types
Accept: application/json

###

### GET literature type by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/literature-types/1
Accept: application/json

###

### CREATE new literature type
POST http://localhost:8080/api/literature-types
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pamatliteratūra",
  "description": "Galvenie mācību materiāli"
}

###

### UPDATE literature type
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/literature-types/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Papildu literatūra",
  "description": "Papildus izziņas avoti"
}

###

### DELETE literature type
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/literature-types/1

###

### GET all literature sources
GET http://localhost:8080/api/literature-sources
Accept: application/json

###

### GET source by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/literature-sources/1
Accept: application/json

###

### CREATE literature source
POST http://localhost:8080/api/literature-sources
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseInfo": {
    "id": "COURSE_INFO_UUID_HERE"
  },
  "type": {
    "id": 1
  },
  "citation": "Latvijas Universitāte. (2021). Datu analīze izglītībā.",
  "url": "https://example.com/avots",
  "language": "lv"
}

###

### UPDATE source
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/literature-sources/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseInfo": {
    "id": "COURSE_INFO_UUID_HERE"
  },
  "type": {
    "id": 1
  },
  "citation": "LU. (2022). Atjaunots avots.",
  "url": "https://example.com/jauns",
  "language": "lv"
}

###

### DELETE source
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/literature-sources/1
